de.dhbw_stuttgart.hb.inf2016.RaumKartierung.Protocol

Interface IToRobotSender


  • public interface IToRobotSender
    Interface for the server endpoint of the robot protocol. Defines methods for sending and receiving messages from an to the robot.
    Author:
    Julian Vogel
